Package com.bytedesk.ai.springai.config

Class ChatClientPrimaryConfig

java.lang.Object
com.bytedesk.ai.springai.config.ChatClientPrimaryConfig
@Configuration public class ChatClientPrimaryConfig extends Object
根据spring.ai.model.chat配置动态设置Primary的ChatClient 支持的值：zhipuai, ollama, dashscope, deepseek, baidu, tencent, volcengine, openai, openrouter, siliconflow, gitee, none
